# GlitchFontChanger
#### A chrome extension that adds two additional buttons on the glitch.com editor to give the ability to the user to change fonts.
![GLitch.com showcase](https://i.imgur.com/tstN5yt.png)

### How to use 
* Clone or download this repo
* go to **[chrome://extensions](chrome://extensions)**
* enable *developer mode*
* Click on load unpacked
* select the whole folder

### Disclaimer
Assets used in this project contain the glitch logo **which I do not own**, if this is a problem you can request a removal and I'll remove it *ASAP*.

